node.text: For #WorldChildrensDay, I spoke to three young people working to reimagine a better world for every child. Gitanjali developed an app to spread kindness in the USA. Emmanuel invented a contactless hand sanitizing machine and teaches at an orphanage in Tanzania. Aibanu helped spread awareness about COVID-19 and mental health in Kazakhstan. Together, they are sharing positivity, love and light and I'm so glad you get to meet them too. @voicesofyouth #ForEveryChild
